{"tid":1563921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於見到跳閘同路人，好感動","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T16:14:59.000Z","uid":30076,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a119a968a6ca56146a273e041182bbf705ce1cef","tid":1563921,"uid":30076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:42:36.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩見個手足係閘口搵黎搵去唔知做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是小弟直接係佢面前跳過，想用行動話比佢知搵唔到八仔，咪直接跳囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢就即刻跳左閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟我真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家夠膽跳既就放膽去跳，同路人見到真係會壯膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚比黨鐵賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足跳完真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fb2e6b55534c8c77744a58ef0d795f84a56153","tid":1563921,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1e6dcd9063a06d9c05c66c0b60c41acc8f961bbb","tid":1563921,"uid":30076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"跳吧跳吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d057e71aec717af2d89c443487e7817bcef6500","tid":1563921,"uid":61960,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"第一次好撚驚<br />\n之後依家跳得好撚爽<br />\n雙手撐住一嘢飛過去嘅感覺真係一試難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cefc76456d495f09a4c5053616da4a4bb44562","tid":1563921,"uid":30076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4d057e71aec717af2d89c443487e7817bcef6500","tid":1563921,"uid":61960,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"第一次好撚驚<br />\n之後依家跳得好撚爽<br />\n雙手撐住一嘢飛過去嘅感覺真係一試難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"係要睇下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你十點幾Foodpanda仲未收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行多兩步咪無人守<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a69276daa724d918e10ec19ac00dd8009fcdd6e","tid":1563921,"uid":61960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"今日個foodpanda係我面前睇地鐵廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef321321bc11ae6f085b6d93ad5a2607af9e6b6","tid":1563921,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"藍田未見過人跳<br />\n不過我跳果陣有著校服既學生叫我加油<br /